    "name": "ExoColony: Planet Survival",
    "steam_appid": 2187340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到这款设定在遥远星球上的挑战性殖民地模拟游戏。</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一小群殖民者开始，你需要开采资源、精炼材料、建造结构，并通过新技术进行创新。跨越世代和世纪，你将把定居点扩展为繁荣的文明，并改造星球使其成为你的新家园。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >跨越时代的繁荣</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >殖民者出生、接受教育、工作、退休和死亡。经过几代人的传承，他们的需求可能会发生变化，奉献精神也可能会减弱。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/6ab0d39178f0668d47699f0657448e5b.poster.avif?t=1749070472\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/6ab0d39178f0668d47699f0657448e5b.webm?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/6ab0d39178f0668d47699f0657448e5b.mp4?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >质量守恒定律</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有任何东西会简单地消失。每一点材料都会转化为新的东西。资源遵循自己的循环，包括生产、消耗和回收。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/ac773d039f384295961858859d0d5d65.poster.avif?t=1749070472\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/ac773d039f384295961858859d0d5d65.webm?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/ac773d039f384295961858859d0d5d65.mp4?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >食物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用周围环境中的材料，将贫瘠的土壤转化为肥沃的农田。融化冰块获得水源，用水种植食物，然后净化水源以便重复使用。平衡这些要素，看着你的殖民地在你生产的食物滋养下茁壮成长。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/9f2319672640f9a8f856c33a23650fe5.poster.avif?t=1749070472\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/9f2319672640f9a8f856c33a23650fe5.webm?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/9f2319672640f9a8f856c33a23650fe5.mp4?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大气层</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将呼出的二氧化碳重新转化为氧气供殖民者使用。解决工业污染问题并管理各种气体。随着基地的扩张，维持大气压力变得至关重要。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/5ea5f5f7913122f72d73ffbcfcf3e7ef.poster.avif?t=1749070472\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/5ea5f5f7913122f72d73ffbcfcf3e7ef.webm?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/5ea5f5f7913122f72d73ffbcfcf3e7ef.mp4?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >工业</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从开采矿石和矿物质开始，将其精炼为建造建筑物和制作物品所必需的高级材料。通过每一步，将原始资源转化为不断扩张的殖民地的基础要素。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/034dd770404f8b9bcec2302005f3dd21.poster.avif?t=1749070472\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/034dd770404f8b9bcec2302005f3dd21.webm?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187340/extras/034dd770404f8b9bcec2302005f3dd21.mp4?t=1749070472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >星球改造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过管理温度控制、生态系统增长和水资源来改造星球表面，使其适宜居住。创造可呼吸的大气层，将星球变成你的新家园。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...以及更多</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>研究：</strong> 通过研究树解锁新的可能性、建筑物和配方。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>电力：</strong> 从多种来源产生和储存能源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>游戏事件：</strong> 宇宙中可能发生奇怪的事情。有些事件可能很好，但有些...你会亲自体验的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>空间管理：</strong> 处理你不需要的材料。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>奢侈食品和商品：</strong> 生产各种物品以保持殖民者的生产力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>空闲时间：</strong> 满足殖民者的社交需求以防止动乱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>温度：</strong> 控制殖民地内部和星球上的温度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地下见！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 捷克语, 波兰语, 日语, 俄语, 简体中文, 法语, 意大利语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
